    • LIST_WILDCARD

      public static final BinaryTagType<BinaryTag> LIST_WILDCARD
      Synthetic tag type used as a list's element type to indicate it contains elements of multiple types.

      This tag type cannot be read or written. List tag serialization will auto-box lists with this element type.

      Since:
      4.21.0
